---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Responsible Gambling | Read Between Bets"
  description="Gambling should be fun and entertaining. Learn about responsible gambling practices and get help if you need it."
  alternates={{ en: '/responsible-gambling/', fr: '/fr/responsible-gambling/' }}
>
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="section-padding max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="mx-auto mb-4 h-16 w-16 rounded-2xl bg-dark-800 border border-dark-700 grid place-items-center"><svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 3l7 4v6c0 5-3 9-7 11C8 22 5 18 5 13V7l7-4z"></path></svg></div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Responsible Gambling</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">Your safety and wellbeing are our priority</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-dark-800 rounded-2xl border border-dark-700 p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Gambling Should Be Fun</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">At Read Between Bets, we believe gambling should always be an enjoyable form of entertainment, never a source of stress or financial problems. If gambling stops being fun, it's time to take a break.</p>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6">
          <div class="bg-dark-900 rounded-xl p-4">
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Avoid</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-400 text-sm space-y-2">
              <li>Chase your losses</li>
              <li>Borrow money to gamble</li>
              <li>Gamble when upset or stressed</li>
              <li>Spend more than your budget</li>
              <li>Think of gambling as a way to make money</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Warning Signs</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Be aware of these common warning signs of problem gambling:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 space-y-2">
            <li>Spending more time or money on gambling than intended</li>
            <li>Difficulty controlling, cutting back, or stopping gambling</li>
            <li>Feeling restless or irritable when trying to reduce gambling</li>
            <li>Gambling to escape problems or relieve negative feelings</li>
            <li>Lying to family or friends about gambling activities</li>
            <li>Jeopardizing relationships, job, or education due to gambling</li>
            <li>Relying on others to bail you out of financial problems caused by gambling</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Self-Exclusion and Tools</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Most reputable online casinos offer responsible gambling tools:</p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-dark-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-dark-700">
              <h3 class="text-brand-400 font-semibold mb-2">Deposit Limits</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Set daily, weekly, or monthly limits on how much you can deposit.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-dark-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-dark-700">
              <h3 class="text-brand-400 font-semibold mb-2">Time Limits</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Set reminders or limits on how long you can play per session.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-dark-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-dark-700">
              <h3 class="text-brand-400 font-semibold mb-2">Self-Exclusion</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Temporarily or permanently block access to your account.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-dark-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-dark-700">
              <h3 class="text-brand-400 font-semibold mb-2">Reality Checks</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Get regular notifications about your time and spending.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-900/30 to-orange-900/30 rounded-2xl border border-red-500/30 p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Need Help?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">If you or someone you know is struggling with gambling addiction, help is available 24/7. These organizations provide confidential support:</p>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <a href="https://www.gamcare.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-dark-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-dark-700 hover:border-brand-500/50 transition-colors">
              <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">GamCare</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-400 text-sm">gamcare.org.uk</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1">UK support and counseling</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.gamblingtherapy.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-dark-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-dark-700 hover:border-brand-500/50 transition-colors">
              <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">Gambling Therapy</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-400 text-sm">gamblingtherapy.org</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1">Global online support</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.gambleaware.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-dark-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-dark-700 hover:border-brand-500/50 transition-colors">
              <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-1">BeGambleAware</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-400 text-sm">begambleaware.org</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1">Information and advice</p>
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-white font-semibold">National Gambling Helpline (UK):</p>
            <a href="tel:0808-8020-133" class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300">0808 8020 133</a>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Free, confidential, 24/7</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Age Verification</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Gambling is strictly for adults aged 18+ (or the legal gambling age in your jurisdiction). We support strict age verification measures and encourage parents to use parental control software to prevent underage access to gambling websites.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Our Commitment</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Read Between Bets is committed to promoting responsible gambling. We:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-300 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>Aim to promote operators that are licensed and regulated where they operate</li>
            <li>Encourage you to verify legality and licensing in your jurisdiction before playing</li>
            <li>Provide accurate information about games and odds</li>
            <li>Never target underage individuals</li>
            <li>Encourage responsible gambling practices</li>
            <li>Provide resources for those who need help</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-500">Remember: <span class="text-white font-semibold">When the fun stops, stop.</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

